high_descs: Turn around, go to the round table.
Pick up the apple on the table, the one closer to the plant.
Bring the apple to the left, across the room to the microwave on the counter.
Heat the apple in the mike.
Bring the heated apple back across the room, to the trash can past the fridge.
Put the heated apple in the trash can, left of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the black table.
Pick up the apple to the right of the white cup.
Walk over to the microwave across the room.
Put the apple inside of the microwave, heat the apple, take the apple out of the microwave.
Turn left and walk back over to the black bin to the left of the fridge.
Put the apple inside of the black bin.
anns.task_desc: To heat up an apple and put it inside of the black bin.

high_descs: Turn back to go the gray table
Pick up an apple from the table
Take the apple and go to microwave across the room
Open the microwave, put the apple in it, warm it for a few seconds, take it out, and close the microwave
Turn around, go back to face the fridge
Put the apple in the bin next to the fridge on the left side
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in the bin
